    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LADEig/status/2034285328635437093",
      "reply_text": "Tiebreaker is a big deal. Lakers need all the help they can get.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T15:59:39.598224+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/StephMuse_/status/2034252596270014764",
      "reply_text": "Curry's got some company now. 👍",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:00:31.203098+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ColdestNBA/status/2034294999462891749",
      "reply_text": "That was a nasty foul. Terry got hurt bad.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:01:06.304367+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/AaronLevine_/status/2034273688582004879",
      "reply_text": "That's a great quote, but we've heard that before. What's changed?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:01:57.757052+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ESPNPR/status/2034272609630572809",
      "reply_text": "Warriors vs Celtics looks like a great matchup. Celtics' defense will be tested.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:02:39.102435+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBABlackburn/status/2034276135631192065",
      "reply_text": "Yeah consistency matters. They can't afford to drop one at home.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:03:34.676488+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/RunBoyRunTTFL/status/2034262050449297445",
      "reply_text": "Love the scoring diversity, but KAT's consistency is still a top-10 asset",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:04:12.395238+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/o_a_khan/status/2034282876976701463",
      "reply_text": "Knueppel's efficiency is insane. 67.6 TS% since the break is elite",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:13:41.915000+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/HYLTSEHUN/status/2034279996714287579",
      "reply_text": "Cortis has had some big NBA moments, but Lolla is a different beast. What's their festival experience?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:14:33.275396+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/AndersPicks/status/2034296115118461206",
      "reply_text": "Fair point about the ORebs, but those 3pt numbers are concerning",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:15:14.513634+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/warriors/status/2034283690910474639",
      "reply_text": "West coast game in Boston. That's a tough one for GSW fans.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:25:10.635188+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/restsinagony/status/2034300023471542629",
      "reply_text": "That's a throwback to the 2023 playoffs",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:27:06.374838+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Arctic__IO/status/2034295539831877641",
      "reply_text": "Those first 3 minutes are crucial. Defense matters in the playoffs.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:27:54.455977+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MugiHoops/status/2034282625435611437",
      "reply_text": "Those numbers are impressive. What's the concern with his game?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:28:33.637296+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JalenWynn/status/2034307793423851967",
      "reply_text": "Big news for the Wings. Hope she's back to form soon.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:39:56.692841+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/_Locksmiths__/status/2034306428333142226",
      "reply_text": "That's a great sample size. His playmaking has been consistent lately.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:40:30.090593+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/tripleMwassup/status/2034279043278004380",
      "reply_text": "Fair, but that's a lot of pressure on one guy. Can he carry the team to the Finals?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:41:14.657998+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MarkG_Medina/status/2034273959081082966",
      "reply_text": "That's what separates the greats from the good. Accountability is key.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T16:42:08.271784+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA/status/2034309406465331616",
      "reply_text": "KD and LeBron have been going at it for a long time",
